snippet.title: Just Hoops - Trickshots | Launch Trailer | Meta Quest Platform
snippet.description:
Experience the ultimate arcade basketball challenge with JUST HOOPS! The Trick Shots update drops December 12th on Meta Quest 3, letting you design and share your own trick shots in mixed reality. Don’t miss this creative twist on Pop-A-Shot! 🏀✨

🎮 Get the game here : https://www.meta.com/experiences/just-hoops/4038407439503919/
